eventDecorators.name: Harvest
eventDecorators.description: Emitted when an update to `requestTokensRemoved` is made. Emitted when the implementation of a variable debt token is upgraded.

functionDecorators.name: harvest
functionDecorators.description: Harvest any profits made converted to the asset and pass them to the caller.

parameterDecorators.name: balance
parameterDecorators.description: The amount of tokens the caller thinks it has invested.

parameterDecorators.name: sender
parameterDecorators.description: The address of the initiator of this transaction. Can be used for reimbursements, etc.

returnDecorators.name: amountAdded
returnDecorators.description: The delta (+profit or -loss) that occured in contrast to `balance`.
